ary: &'static str`, `final_review_enabled: bool`\n- Used in flow definitions\n\n**FlowDefinition (struct)**:\n- Fields: `preset: FlowPreset`, `description: &'static str`, `stages: &'static [StageId]`, `validation_profile: ValidationProfile`\n\n### 4. Module Structure in src/\n\n**lib.rs**: Module declarations:\n```rust\npub mod adapters;\npub mod cli;\npub mod contexts;\npub mod shared;\n```\n\n**main.rs**: Async entry point with tracing initialization, CLI parsing via clap\n\n**shared/domain.rs**: All domain types and constants\n\n**shared/error.rs**: AppError enum with thiserror, AppResult type alias\n- Error types: AlreadyInitialized, WorkspaceConflict, InvalidStageCursorField, InvalidIdentifier, InvalidFlowPreset, UnsupportedWorkspaceVersion, NotYetImplemented, Io, TomlDeserialize, TomlSerialize\n\n**cli/mod.rs**: CLI router:\n- Cli struct with clap Parser\n- Commands enum: Init, Flow, Config, Project, Run, Requirements, Daemon, Conformance\n- async run() dispatcher\n\n**CLI Subcommands** (mostly returning NotYetImplemented):\n- `flow list/show` - Implemented\n- `init` - Implemented\n- `config show/get/set/edit` - Not yet implemented\n- `project create/select/list/show/delete` - Not yet implemented\n- `run start/resume/status/history/tail/rollback` - Not yet implemented\n- `requirements draft/quick/show/answer` - Not yet implemented\n- `daemon start/status/abort/retry/reconcile` - Not yet implemented\n- `conformance list/run` - Not yet implemented\n\n**contexts/workflow_composition/mod.rs**: Flow definitions\n- 4 static flow definitions with stage sequences\n- Functions: `built_in_flows()`, `flow_definition()`, `flow_definition_by_id()`\n- Stage sequences:\n  - **Standard**: 8 stages (PromptReview → Planning → Implementation → Qa → Review → CompletionPanel → AcceptanceQa → FinalReview)\n  - **QuickDev**: 4 stages (PlanAndImplement → Review → ApplyFixes → FinalReview)\n  - **DocsChange**: 4 stages (DocsPlan → DocsUpdate → DocsValidation → Review)\n  - **CiImprovement**: 4 stages (CiPlan → CiUpdate → CiValidation → Review)\n\n**contexts/workspace_governance/mod.rs**: Workspace initialization\n- Constants: `WORKSPACE_DIR = \".ralph-burning\"`, `WORKSPACE_CONFIG_FILE = \"workspace.toml\"`\n- Required directories: `[\"projects\", \"requirements\", \"daemon/tasks\", \"daemon/leases\"]`\n- Functions:\n  - `initialize_workspace()` - Creates workspace structure\n  - `load_workspace_config()` - Reads workspace.toml\n  - `ensure_supported_workspace_version()` - Version validation\n\n**contexts/{agent_execution, automation_runtime, conformance_spec, project_run_record, requirements_drafting}/mod.rs**: \n- Minimal files with only `const CONTEXT_NAME: &str`\n- Placeholders for future implementation\n\n**adapters/fs.rs**: FileSystem adapter\n- `create_workspace()` - Creates directories and workspace.toml\n- `read_to_string()` - File reading\n- `render_workspace_config()` - TOML serialization\n\n### 5. Test Files\n\n**tests/unit/domain_test.rs**: StageCursor tests\n- Validates zero-field rejection\n- Tests cursor advancement (cycle, attempt, completion_round independence)\n\n**tests/unit/flow_preset_test.rs**: FlowPreset and flow definition tests\n- All 4 presets registered in order\n- Each preset's stage sequence verification\n\n**tests/unit/workspace_test.rs**: Workspace initialization tests\n- Config serialization round-trip\n- Directory structure creation\n- Duplicate initialization prevention\n\n**tests/cli.rs**: CLI integration tests\n- `flow list` - Outputs all presets\n- `flow show` - Shows stage sequences\n- Invalid flow handling\n- `init` - Creates workspace layout\n- Prevents re-initialization\n\n**tests/conformance/features/**: Gherkin specs\n- flow_discovery.feature: Flow listing and showing\n- workspace_init.feature: Workspace initialization scenarios\n\n### 6. Key Constants and Values\n\n- Workspace version: 1\n- Flow presets: 4 (Standard, QuickDev, DocsChange, CiImprovement)\n- Stage types: 16 distinct stage IDs\n- Workspa