s` | Added `ContractError` enum with `failure_class()` and `stage_id()` methods |\n| `src/contexts/workflow_composition/mod.rs` | Exposed `contracts`, `payloads`, `renderers` modules |\n| `src/contexts/workflow_composition/payloads.rs` | **New** — 3 payload types, `ReviewOutcome`, `StepStatus`, `StagePayload` enum |\n| `src/contexts/workflow_composition/contracts.rs` | **New** — `StageContract`, `ContractFamily`, registry, evaluation pipeline |\n| `src/contexts/workflow_composition/renderers.rs` | **New** — deterministic Markdown renderers per family |\n| `tests/unit.rs` | Registered `stage_contract_test` and `renderer_test` modules |\n| `tests/unit/stage_contract_test.rs` | **New** — 27 tests for contracts |\n| `tests/unit/renderer_test.rs` | **New** — 14 tests for renderers |\n| `tests/conformance/features/stage_contracts.feature` | **New** — 9 Gherkin scenarios |"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1260,"cache_read_input_tokens":79350,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1260},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"50421a6e-e879-47e1-9362-86cf29dfc606","uuid":"115438a8-953a-47d3-ad27-d55184c658f1"}
